| **48-72 Hours** | **Access Review:** Audit all CyberArk vaults for standing privileges. Revoke all non-essential service accounts. Perform a final vulnerability scan via Nessus to confirm hardening status. | CISO Security Audit Team |

**Final Directive:** All delivery center heads are required to sign off on the "Hardening Compliance Report" by EOD Friday. Non-compliance will result in immediate network revocation for the offending delivery center. 

*Stay vigilant. Security is a continuous process, not a destination.*

